TEXT.S:
:Macbeth ( Make-pay ) nu ( inggu a kamu : Macbeth ) u masaapuyuan kalabades niSase-piya iti nugikian, u sakanamuhan nu mimelaway a piigiannu kasacacayan. sanisani sa kaladihingan ku pigiki ilabu malabades aca, u sakatawidan ku nikasaditan i piigikian, lalekalan nina giki a kitidaan sa i Su-kelan, sipakay nu gikiay a nipadadan, miawas tu balucu'ay matatebing atu sakay nu cen-ceay madademec, mitapal tu pilungucan tu sikaidaw nu tatungusan miales tu masametekay kacikiyan sadikuday a sakatademaw.
